OL,3,CThree more charged following violent
OL,4,Cdisorder over Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThree further people have been charged
OL,7,Ffollowing the violent disorder in
OL,8,FSouthampton this week in response to
OL,9,Fthe murder of Henry Nowak.
OL,11,FConnor Bishop, 24, of Oxford Street,
OL,12,FSouthampton, Reece Robinson, 21, of
OL,13,FSoberton Road, Havant and Noah
OL,14,FEtherington, 18, of Rowbury Road,
OL,15,FHavant, have been charged with violent
OL,16,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
