OL,3,CThree more charged following violent
OL,4,Cdisorder over Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FFollowing the charges being authorised
OL,7,Fby the Crown Prosecution Service, they
OL,8,Fare due to appear at Southampton
OL,9,FMagistrate's Court this morning
OL,10,F(Friday 5 June).
OL,12,FYesterday 44-year-old Daniel Frost
OL,13,Ffrom Southampton pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fviolent disorder following the unrest
OL,15,Fon Tuesday night.
OL,17,FA second man, 50-year-old Matt Styler
OL,18,Ffrom Gosport, pleaded not guilty to
OL,19,Fassaulting a police officer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
